# THIS IS NOT A REAL KEY.
#
# Public key used by community-service to verify JWTs issued by auth-service.
# Must be a copy of the public.pem matching the auth-service private key
# (see apps/auth-service/src/main/resources/keys/private.pem.example).
#
# Local development:
#   cp apps/auth-service/src/main/resources/keys/public.pem \
#      apps/community-service/src/main/resources/keys/public.pem
#
# Production:
#   Supplied at runtime via JWT_PUBLIC_KEY_PATH env var pointing at the
#   filesystem path of the secret-store-mounted public key.
